  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>The spider is a patient hunter, sensing foes that struggle in its webs.</em><br><br><strong>Minor Form: </strong>You gain a +2 competence bonus on Climb checks, Stealth checks, saving throws against web effects (magical or otherwise), and checks to break free of webs.</p>\n<p>This bonus increases to +4 at 8th level and +6 at 15th level.<br><br><strong>Major Form:</strong> Your shape changes to that of a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant%20Spider\">giant spider</a>. While in this form, you gain darkvision with a range of 60 feet,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/UMR.aspx?ItemName=Tremorsense\">tremorsense</a>&nbsp;with a range of 10 feet, a climb speed of 30 feet, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/UMR.aspx?ItemName=Web\">web</a>&nbsp;special attack, and a bite attack (1d6).</p>\n<p>At 8th level, you gain a +4 racial bonus on Perception checks, and the range of your tremorsense increases to 20 feet.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Improved%20Natural%20Attack\">Improved Natural Attack (bite)</a>, and the range of your tremorsense increases to 30 feet.<br><br><strong>Alternate Natural Attacks:</strong> Bite (B, P, S)</p>",
